high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink
Pick up the knife from under the tomato in the sink
Turn right towards the fridge
Open the fridge, cut the lettuce into slices, close the door
move slightly to the left
Open the fridge, put the knife in to the left of the lettuce then close door
Move slightly to the right again
Open fridge, take a slice of lettuce, close fridge
Turn around and go left around the island in the middle of the room and turn left to face the table
Put the lettuce in the bowl
Pick up the bowl with the lettuce inside
Go left around the island and back to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the bowl with the lettuce to the left of the knife and close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Preparing lettuce to put in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the table, hang a right, go forward, hang a left and go to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is in the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge that is on the left.
Open the fridge, use the knife to cut the lettuce inside the fridge into slices, close the fridge.
Move over to the left side of the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge to the left of the lettuce.
Move over to the right side of the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up a slice of the lettuce that is inside.
Turn around and head to the stove, hang a left and go to the bowl that is on the table to the left.
Put the lettuce in the bowl that is on the table.
Pick up the bowl containing the lettuce from the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a right and go to the fridge.
Put the bowl containing the lettuce inside the fridge to the left of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and bowl containing lettuce inside a fridge.

high_descs: Walk towards the sink
Grab the knife from the sink
Walk with the knife towards the fridge
Slice the lettuce on the fridge
Turn left and walk towards the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Close the fridge, walk away from the fridge and open it again
Grab a lettuce slice from the fridge
Walk towards the island table in the middle
Put the lettuce slice in the bowl on the table
Pick up the bowl from the table
Walk with the bowl towards the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, grab a slice of lettuce, put it in the bowl, put bowl in the fridge
